2017-06-06 12:33:23 +0300 Josef 'Jeff' Sipek <jeff.sipek@dovecot.fi> (0d1b8b6be)

    global: start relying on timeout_remove(NULL) being a no-op

    Cleanup performed with the following semantic patch:

    	@@
    expression E;
    @@

    	- if (E != NULL) {
    - 	timeout_remove(&E);
    - }
    + timeout_remove(&E);

