2016-12-18 13:20:20 +0100 Stephan Bosch <stephan.bosch@dovecot.fi> (08cb8e0ae)

    lib: Created i_zero() wrapper for memset(p, 0, sizeof(*p)).

    Also creates an i_zero_safe() version for safe_memset().

M	src/lib/macros.h

