2016-11-04 12:36:19 +0200 Timo Sirainen <timo.sirainen@dovecot.fi> (6264b51bc)

    lib-storage: Renamed MAIL_SEARCH_ARG_FLAG_USE_TZ to _FLAG_UTC_TIMES


M	src/lib-storage/index/index-search.c
