    global: freshen copyright Robomatically:   git ls-files | xargs perl -p -i
    -e 's/(\d+)-201[0-4]/$1-2015/g;s/ (201[0-4]) Dovecot/ $1-2015 Dovecot/'

    Happy 2015 everyone!

    Signed-off-by: Phil Carmody <phil@dovecot.fi>

