2012-08-19 14:21:37 +0300 Timo Sirainen <tss@iki.fi> (4ee00532a)

    Array API changed: ARRAY_DEFINE(name, type) -> ARRAY(type) name Easy way to
    update your existing code: perl -i -pe 's:ARRAY_DEFINE\(([^,]+),
    *([^)]+)\);:ARRAY($2) $1;:' **/*.[ch]


